'======================ZOMBIE MOVEMENT=================================

Sub ZombieMovement

  If playerCX-45 > ZombieCX then

    ZombieX = 1

  ElseIf playerCX < ZombieCX-45 then

    ZombieX = -1

  elseif ZombieCX > playerCX-45 and ZombieCX < playerCX+45 then

    ZombieX = 0

  endif

endsub



